name: Miabella 1/5 Carat T.W. Diamond 10kt Rose Gold Semi-Eternity Anniversary Ring

reviews.name: Miabella 1/5 Carat T.W. Diamond 10kt Rose Gold Semi-Eternity Anniversary Ring
reviews.reviewText: I bought this to use as a band for another ring I purchased . I was disappointed to see that the ring does not look the same as it does in the picture and video. The diamonds look smaller and are cloudy. The pink gold is nice and it does go with my other ring well. I had a feeling that it wouldn't be the best quality when I bought this item, so overall I am satisfied with my purchase.
reviews.title: You get what you pay for!

reviews.name: Miabella 1/5 Carat T.W. Diamond 10kt Rose Gold Semi-Eternity Anniversary Ring
reviews.reviewText: I've been staring at this ring on walmart website for sometime now and let me just say its so much better on my finger. Its everything and more. So beautiful, the color of the band is great and the quality of the diamonds are beyond my expectations. Would recommend this ring to anyone.
reviews.title: Stunning

reviews.name: Miabella 1/5 Carat T.W. Diamond 10kt Rose Gold Semi-Eternity Anniversary Ring
reviews.reviewText: Purchased two of these of for my upcoming wedding. I love them . Dainty and feminine. Nice quality.
